<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 03:14:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美联储降息疑虑再度浮现，债券收益率攀升，股市承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-29/</link><description>由于数据引发了人们对美联储降息时机和幅度的新疑虑，美国国债收益率周三升至近四周高点，提振了亚太地区国债和美元，同时给股市带来压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国演习更多是为了恐吓、宣传而不是发动战争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-drills-more-about-intimidation-propaganda-than-starting-war-2024-05-29/</link><description>台湾最高安全官员周三表示，中国上周的军事演习更多的是为了宣传和恐吓，而不是发动战争，但中国军队确实展示了他们如何能够极其迅速地做出反应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:12:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-drills-more-about-intimidation-propaganda-than-starting-war-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>通胀数据公布前美元稳定，日元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ahead-inflation-data-yen-wobbles-2024-05-29/</link><description>美元周三保持稳定，因押注美联储在今年晚些时候之前不太可能降息，本周将公布关键通胀数据，而日元则跌至四个星期以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ahead-inflation-data-yen-wobbles-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>继第一季度“强劲”之后，国际货币基金组织上调中国2024年和2025年GDP增​​长预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/imf-upgrades-chinas-2024-2025-gdp-growth-forecasts-after-strong-q1-2024-05-29/</link><description>国际货币基金组织(International Monetary Fund)周三表示，继第一季度“强劲”之后，中国经济今年将增长5%，上调了此前增长4.6%的预测，但预计未来几年增长将放缓。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/imf-upgrades-chinas-2024-2025-gdp-growth-forecasts-after-strong-q1-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>巴西国会提出对低成本在线订单征税的法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/brazils-congress-advances-bill-tax-low-cost-online-orders-2024-05-29/</link><description>巴西国会下议院周二批准了一项法案的主要文本，该法案将对 50 美元以下的国际网上购物征收 20% 的新进口税，大大低于最初提议的较高税率。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/brazils-congress-advances-bill-tax-low-cost-online-orders-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>台湾政府拒绝有争议的议会改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-government-reject-contested-parliament-reforms-2024-05-29/</link><description>台湾内阁将拒绝并发回审查反对派周二通过的有关议会改革的立法，该法案已导致数万人走上街头抗议并指责中国干涉。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 01:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-government-reject-contested-parliament-reforms-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本消费者、澳大利亚消费者物价指数 (CPI) 成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 21:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国因与新冠病毒相关的欺诈和炸弹威胁而对中国个人实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-sanctions-chinese-individuals-over-covid-related-fraud-bomb-threats-2024-05-28/</link><description>美国财政部周二对三名中国个人和三家泰国公司实施制裁，称其参与网络犯罪网络，该网络发出炸弹威胁和欺诈性申请与新冠病毒相关的援助，导致政府损失数十亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:36:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-sanctions-chinese-individuals-over-covid-related-fraud-bomb-threats-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>赫斯股东批准与雪佛龙合并</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-shareholders-approve-merger-with-chevron-2024-05-28/</link><description>根据初步投票结果，赫斯公司周二批准了该公司与美国第二大石油公司雪佛龙价值 530 亿美元的合并。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-shareholders-approve-merger-with-chevron-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>网球-德约科维奇和萨巴伦卡在法国网球公开赛的雨天中轻松度过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/ruud-sabalenka-light-up-roland-garros-after-rain-wreaks-havoc-schedule-2024-05-28/</link><description>法网第三天的降雨给法网带来了一些影响，但卫冕冠军诺瓦克·德约科维奇避免陷入困境，因为他对职业时代创纪录的第25个大满贯冠军的追求在周二有了一个足够坚实的开局。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:59:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/ruud-sabalenka-light-up-roland-garros-after-rain-wreaks-havoc-schedule-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>爱沙尼亚称中国尚未回应海底电缆调查请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/estonia-says-china-has-not-responded-subsea-cables-probe-request-2024-05-28/</link><description>爱沙尼亚国家检察官表示，中国尚未回应六个月前就调查一艘中国船只的请求，爱沙尼亚怀疑这艘船切断了其两条海底电信电缆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:42:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/estonia-says-china-has-not-responded-subsea-cables-probe-request-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车将开发低成本电动汽车应对中国竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-develop-entry-level-electric-vehicles-around-20000-euros-2024-05-28/</link><description>欧洲最大的汽车制造商在本月初与雷诺合作该项目的谈判破裂后，周二表示，大众汽车将开发低成本电动汽车，以更好地与激烈的中国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-develop-entry-level-electric-vehicles-around-20000-euros-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京拒绝美国对中国生产过剩的评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-putin-rejects-us-assessment-chinas-overproduction-2024-05-28/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京驳斥了美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦对中国产能过剩和汽车生产过剩对全球经济影响的担忧，认为这种担忧是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-putin-rejects-us-assessment-chinas-overproduction-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：阿根廷有望于七月开始向中国出口玉米——谷物商会负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/argentina-track-start-corn-exports-china-july-grains-chamber-head-2024-05-28/</link><description>阿根廷粮食出口商会周二告诉路透社，阿根廷有望从 7 月份开始向中国出口期待已久的玉米，这对这个世界第一大南美国家来说将是一个重大推动。 3 粮食供应商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/argentina-track-start-corn-exports-china-july-grains-chamber-head-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国法院将于 9 月听取对 TikTok 潜在禁令的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-hear-challenges-potential-tiktok-ban-september-2024-05-28/</link><description>美国上诉法院周二制定了一个快速通道时间表，以考虑一项新法律的法律挑战，该法律要求中国字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok 在美国的资产，否则将面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-hear-challenges-potential-tiktok-ban-september-2024-05-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>